Live Music Night at Bowery Ballroom

Join us for an incredible evening of live music featuring local artists on Saturday, November 9, 2025 at 8:00 PM. Doors open at 7:30 PM. Tickets are $25-$35. The event will be held at our venue located at 6 Delancey St, Lower East Side, New York, NY 10002. This is an all-ages event with a full bar available. Get your tickets now!
